<div class="jumbotron">
  <div class="center">
      <div class="scrim light-txt main-font">
        <h1>Meet Matt</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="center light-txt main-font scrim">
        <a href="#about"><input type="button" value="Read My Story" class="btn btn-default btn-lg clear light-txt" style="margin-top: 30px; transition: background-color 1s, color 0.5s"></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="pane" style="padding-top: 15px !important;">
  <a name="about"></a>
  <div class="contain">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span4">
          <h1 class="green-txt btm-pding" style="margin-left: 10px;">My Story</h1>
          <div class="float-left">
            <%= link_to(image_tag("matt.jpeg", :alt => "logo", :title => "Home", :class=>"responsive small-img", :style=>"margin-right: 50px; margin-top: 10px;"), "#about") %>
          </div>
        </div>
      <div class="span8">
        <h3 class="med-weight">Tech Geek + Adventurer</h3>
        <p class="light-weight">
          I spent the years after I graduated college searching for work that I found meaningful. It was a journey that involved all sorts of jobs and projects - from to teaching English overseas and guiding outdoor education programs, to helping Fortune 500 companies build sustainability initiatives, and developing the product roadmap for an early-stage startup.  Away from work, I'm an avid traveler, an outdoor enthusiast, and a huge fan of spicy foods.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<a name="work"></a>
  <div class="pane white-bg">
    <div class="contain">
      <div class="row-fluid">
          <div class="span8">
            <h1 class="med-flat-blue-txt" style="text-align: right; margin-right: 40px;">Work</h1>
            <div class="float-right">
              <%= link_to(image_tag("html.png", :alt => "logo", :title => "Home", :class=>"responsive small-img", :style=>"margin-left: 25px; margin-top: 25px;"), "#work") %>
            </div>
          </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h3 class="med-weight">Startup Product Teams Are Neat</h3>
          <p class="light-weight">
            I love finding new ways to solve problems with technology. I'm just as excited about talking with users and digging into their needs as I am about writing code for new features. My previous role as a Product Manager was to discover what made our users tick and ensure that we built useful products for them.  Today, I'm focused on learning full stack web development at the Turing School of Software Design.  During this 7-month immersive program, my emphasis will be on learning how to build scalable Ruby on Rails web applications.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<a name="play"></a>
<div class="pane">
  <div class="contain">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span4">
          <h1 class="green-txt btm-pding" style="margin-left: 50px;">Play</h1>
          <div class="float-left">
            <%= link_to(image_tag("mountains.png", :alt => "logo", :title => "Home", :class=>"responsive small-img", :style=>"margin-right: 50px;"), "#play") %>
          </div>
        </div>
      <div class="span8">
        <h3 class="med-weight">The Outdoors are Fun</h3>
        <p class="light-weight">
          When I'm not working on tech, you'll find me getting away from the city to recharge.  When it's warm outside, I spend my free time backpacking, mountain biking, or rock climbing. And more recently, I've taken up a new hobby in learning how to kiteboard.  In the wintertime, I'm always chasing big storms in search of deep powder turns.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

